Again, we consider the binarized version of the Olive Oil dataset in Table 3 as a market basket problem consisting of N = 11 transactions o1, ..., o11 and M = 8 items f1, ..., f8. We want to apply the Apriori algorithm (the specific variant described in Chapter 21 of the lecture notes) to find all itemsets with support greater than epsilon = 0.3. What is the content of L3 when the Apriori algorithm is completed?

A. L3 = {}
B. L3 = {{f3, f6, f8}}
C. L3 = {{f2, f6, f8}, {f3, f6, f8}}
D. L3 = {{f2}, {f3}, {f6}, {f8}}
